metadata.description: Euro Heroes are a collection of 333 pixel figures on the Ethereum blockchain that include traits from European warriors throughout history bringing them to life in the Web3 world. Euro Heroes give off pure Web3 vibes. No Politics. No BS. This project is public domain, feel free to use Euro Heroes any way you would like. Holding a Euro Hero also provides holders with a top-tier alpha group posting investment calls, profitable drops on all blockchains, and one-on-one help. Holding two Euro Heroes guarantee you a whitelist spot to the upcoming collection RapStars which is a music utility NFT providing an Alpha Group, Whitelist tool, and a music marketplace.
